  "text": "There are several works researching on optimizing the user scheduling and UAV trajectory to increase the minimum average rate and throughput per user. The main objective of these papers is to minimize the number of required UAVs to cover a specific area with a multi-UAV network [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] . Autonomous flying approaches in a network of multiple UAVs to optimally locate the UAVs in the network are described in [CITATION_3] . In [CITATION_4] , the propagation loss and the interference caused by all UAVs in a multi-UAV network have been studied.",
